## Together: ChocoMarket

Together, we will select architectural styles for the ChocoMarket case study.

{% linkcard title="ChocoMarket GitHub repository" href="https://github.com/unideb-advanced-software-engineering/26-spring-00-chocomarket" /%}

## Together: Architecture Styles Worksheet

We will select an architectural style for new, short case studies using Mark Richards' [Architecture Styles Worksheet](/site/architecture-styles-worksheet.pdf).

The procedure for this group activity is as follows:
- Each group receives the same case study.
- The groups spend a few minutes identifying characteristics and selecting an architectural style (or styles).
- We discuss together which styles each group chose and why.

{% linkcard
   title="Architecture Styles Worksheet"
   href="/site/architecture-styles-worksheet.pdf"
   target="_blank" /%}

