## Homework

Groups will choose an architectural style (or styles) for their case studies.

The chosen style must be documented in the group's GitHub repository as follows:

{% filetree %}
- ac.md
- **as.md** The file containing the chosen style(s).
- asr.md
- case-study.md
- README.md
- srs.doc
{% /filetree %}

{% aside type="tip" %}
For inspiration regarding the file contents, check out the [ChocoMarket repository](https://github.com/unideb-advanced-software-engineering/26-spring-00-chocomarket/blob/main/as.md).
{% /aside %}
